### Atualizar sensor existente
PUT http://localhost:8080/sensors/2
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "type": "UMIDADE",
  "measurementUnit": "%",
  "lastValue": 65.2,
  "status": "ERROR",
  "minLimit": 20.0,
  "maxLimit": 80.0,
